msgid "To get started, let's set your language and location."
msgstr "始めるには、言語と場所を設定しましょう。"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/christmas.tsx:110
msgid "Today, an estimated 350 million real Christmas trees are grown across Europe alone, most of them farmed specifically for the season."
msgstr "今日、ヨーロッパだけで推定3億5千万本の本物のクリスマスツリーが栽培されており、そのほとんどがこのシーズンのために特別に農場で育てられています。"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/total-solar-eclipse.tsx:57
msgid "Today, many people travel great distances to stand within the path of totality."
msgstr "今日では、多くの人が皆既帯の中に立つために遠くまで旅をします。"

#: src/pages/feedback/index.tsx:307
#~ msgid "Too much battery usage"
#~ msgstr "過度のバッテリー使用"

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:190
msgid "Total Lunar Eclipse"
msgstr "皆既月食"

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:191
msgid "Total Solar Eclipse"
msgstr "皆既日食"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/lunar-new-year.tsx:85
msgid "Traditional stories of the monster Nian are said to have inspired the use of loud sounds, firecrackers, and the colour red as symbols of protection and good fortune."
msgstr "怪物ニエンの伝承は、大きな音や爆竹、赤い色を魔除けと幸運の象徴として用いる由来になったと言われています。"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/hanukkah.tsx:99
msgid "Traditions"
msgstr "伝統"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/spring-equinox.tsx:106
msgid "Traditions such as Nowruz continue to celebrate themes of renewal on or around the equinox."
msgstr "ノウルーズのような伝統は、春分の前後に再生のテーマを祝う行事として今も続いています。"

#: src/features/settings/ui/initialisation.tsx:202
msgid "Try again"
msgstr "もう一度試す"

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:114
msgid "Tuesday"
